            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/mobile/smartphone">Smartphone</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Currently available for Switch.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > THQ Nordic [553 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/thq-nordic">THQ Nordic</a> will release <em><a title="Games > Gothic Classic [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gothic-classic">Gothic Classic</a></em> for iOS in 2026, the publisher announced. <span id="more-1033887"></span></p><p><em>Gothic Classic</em> first launched for Switch on September 28, 2023. PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One versions are <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/gothic-classic-trilogy-coming-to-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-and-xbox-one-in-2026">also due out</a> in 2026 alongside <em><a title="Games > Gothic II Complete Classic [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gothic-ii-complete-classic">Gothic II Complete Classic</a></em> and <em><a title="Games > Gothic 3 Classic [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gothic-3-classic">Gothic 3 Classic</a></em>.</p><p>The original <em>Gothic</em> launched on March 15, 2001, making yesterday its 25th anniversary.</p><p>A full remake, <em><a title="Games > Gothic Remake [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gothic-remake">Gothic Remake</a></em>, is <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2026/02/gothic-remake-launches-june-5">due out</a> for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1297900/Gothic_1_Remake/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.gog.com/en/game/gothic_1_remake" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GOG</a> on June 5.</p><p>Watch a teaser trailer for the iOS version below.</p><h2><span>iOS Announce Trailer</span></h2><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><iframe title="Gothic Classic | Mobile Announcement Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rBoGGutUZ4I?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/03/gothic-classic-coming-to-ios-in-2026]]></content:encoded>
